```mermaid
graph TD;
   Start 
   accept_three_numbers_as_input
   set all as unchecked 
   start sorting all numbers from largest
   if first is greater that second and third number, set first number as large and checked
   if not, check first if the number is less than both second and third numbers, if so set first number as small and checked
   store result
   check if there is next number
   repeat from step 4
   if no next number, output result and End
   END-->Start
```
